Berenice Epideires (Giriig: Βερενίκη ἐπὶ Δειρῆς, Steph. B. sv; Strabo xvi pp. 769, 773; Mela, iii 8; Plin vi 34; Ptol viii 16 § 12), ama "Berenice upon Ceelka Dhulka ", wuxuu ahaa magaalo ku taal xeebta galbeed ee Badda Cas. Waxay ku taallaa meel u dhow [[Bab-el-Mandeb]], oo ah [[Jabuuti]] casriga ah ee casriga ah. Mawqifka dejinta ee xayawaanka boodhka ah ama jilicsanaanta ayaa sabab u ahaa jahawareerkiisa gaarka ah. Hase yeeshee, qaar ka mid ah masuuliyiinta, waxay u adeegsadeen magaca deriska ee magaalo aad u qiime badan oo magaciisu yahay Deire (ama Deira); laakiin xaaladda dhabta ah ee dambe ee aan la ogeyn.
